1
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:39,999
=The Litchi Road=

2
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:42,940
(A Big Black Carp)

3
00:01:43,660 --> 00:01:45,140
(Ten Years Ago)

4
00:01:45,140 --> 00:01:46,200
- Hello.
- I can walk. Let go!

5
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,700
- You two...
- Ask Chief to be the judge.

6
00:01:47,700 --> 00:01:48,540
Chief is here.

7
00:01:49,770 --> 00:01:50,610
Chief, look.

8
00:01:50,780 --> 00:01:52,180
- Chief, look.
- How insolent.

9
00:01:56,180 --> 00:01:57,020
Stop.

10
00:02:00,980 --> 00:02:01,820
Who are you?

11
00:02:02,900 --> 00:02:03,740
He's new.

12
00:02:03,860 --> 00:02:06,380
The academic division's Li...

13
00:02:06,380 --> 00:02:07,955
The mathematics division's Li Shande.

14
00:02:07,980 --> 00:02:09,740
Instead of being on duty
at Leyou Garden,

15
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,444
why are you back at Shanglin Office?

16
00:02:11,540 --> 00:02:12,940
- He put poison.
- Nonsense.

17
00:02:12,940 --> 00:02:14,977
- Poison? Don't talk nonsense.
- You put poison.

18
00:02:15,020 --> 00:02:15,900
Chief.

19
00:02:15,900 --> 00:02:17,740
Today,
we went to Leyou Garden to release fish.

20
00:02:17,740 --> 00:02:18,580
I just got the basin

21
00:02:18,580 --> 00:02:19,500
off the cart.

22
00:02:19,620 --> 00:02:20,460
When I turned around,

23
00:02:20,540 --> 00:02:21,660
I saw scattered leaves

24
00:02:21,660 --> 00:02:23,380
floating in the water.

25
00:02:23,540 --> 00:02:24,733
They're Chinese toon shoots!

26
00:02:25,180 --> 00:02:26,540
It's harmless to humans

27
00:02:26,700 --> 00:02:27,660
but deadly to fish.

28
00:02:27,980 --> 00:02:28,820
Carps

29
00:02:29,020 --> 00:02:30,220
are different from other fish.

30
00:02:30,580 --> 00:02:31,420
When carps

31
00:02:31,420 --> 00:02:32,820
see something moving on the water,

32
00:02:32,820 --> 00:02:34,090
they'll jump up and take a bite.

33
00:02:34,090 --> 00:02:35,060
People don't understand.

34
00:02:35,060 --> 00:02:37,577
That's why there's the saying
"a carp leaping over the dragon gate".

35
00:02:37,577 --> 00:02:38,300
Alright.

36
00:02:38,300 --> 00:02:39,140
Chief.

37
00:02:39,377 --> 00:02:41,866
Uphold justice for me, Chief.

38
00:02:41,900 --> 00:02:43,022
Uphold justice for me too.

39
00:03:02,555 --> 00:03:04,780
It must be your fault.
You want to poison these carps

40
00:03:04,860 --> 00:03:05,700
and

41
00:03:05,700 --> 00:03:07,940
ask Shanglin Office to buy new carps.

42
00:03:08,060 --> 00:03:09,530
You'll then benefit from it.

43
00:03:09,660 --> 00:03:11,088
I ask for your wise judgment.

44
00:03:11,260 --> 00:03:12,580
This is slander.

45
00:03:13,220 --> 00:03:14,100
Alright.

46
00:03:14,260 --> 00:03:15,100
If it's true,

47
00:03:15,133 --> 00:03:16,280
you'll be punished severely.

48
00:03:17,460 --> 00:03:20,100
If you accused Supervisor Song wrongly,

49
00:03:20,500 --> 00:03:21,844
you'll be fined one month's pay.

50
00:03:22,140 --> 00:03:23,100
One month?

51
00:03:24,740 --> 00:03:25,580
One...

52
00:03:25,740 --> 00:03:26,940
One month is...

53
00:03:29,700 --> 00:03:30,540
You two.

54
00:03:30,740 --> 00:03:32,060
Why get upset

55
00:03:32,180 --> 00:03:33,220
over a carp?

56
00:03:34,740 --> 00:03:35,620
This guy

57
00:03:35,620 --> 00:03:37,380
just joined Shanglin Office.

58
00:03:37,660 --> 00:03:38,888
He doesn't know the rules yet.

59
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,980
He's young and impulsive.
I can understand that.

60
00:03:40,980 --> 00:03:42,380
How about you both meet halfway?

61
00:03:49,260 --> 00:03:50,100
Forget it.

62
00:03:51,620 --> 00:03:52,460
Liangyuan.

63
00:03:52,820 --> 00:03:53,660
Calm down.

64
00:03:54,700 --> 00:03:55,540
I

65
00:03:55,780 --> 00:03:56,620
shouldn't have

66
00:03:57,220 --> 00:03:58,060
hit you today.

67
00:03:59,060 --> 00:03:59,900
Here.

68
00:03:59,940 --> 00:04:01,380
These two Songjiang perches

69
00:04:02,020 --> 00:04:03,140
are my apology.

70
00:04:06,980 --> 00:04:09,740
No, Songjiang perch
is a specialty of Huating County.

71
00:04:10,660 --> 00:04:12,822
None on the market
is supplied to Eastern Palace.

72
00:04:13,380 --> 00:04:15,180
Is this
from Shanglin Office's ice storage?

73
00:04:15,300 --> 00:04:17,149
It is said
that Shanglin Office's ice storage

74
00:04:17,150 --> 00:04:19,460
is all fruits and vegetables
from various prefectures.

75
00:04:19,866 --> 00:04:20,980
They're all very precious,

76
00:04:20,980 --> 00:04:21,820
especially...

77
00:04:24,780 --> 00:04:25,620
I'm of low ranking.

78
00:04:25,860 --> 00:04:27,155
I dare not eat.

79
00:04:34,940 --> 00:04:36,620
I ask for your wise judgment.

80
00:04:37,260 --> 00:04:39,220
If I falsely accuse him,

81
00:04:39,288 --> 00:04:41,022
I'm willing to be fined
one month's salary.

82
00:04:41,100 --> 00:04:41,940
Chief.

83
00:04:41,980 --> 00:04:44,060
If it is found that I did it,

84
00:04:44,133 --> 00:04:46,000
I will also accept the punishment.

85
00:04:47,911 --> 00:04:48,940
Chief, you can't drink.

86
00:04:49,820 --> 00:04:51,020
You just ate a golden peach.

87
00:04:51,177 --> 00:04:52,600
Golden peach is warm in nature.

88
00:04:52,666 --> 00:04:53,666
If you mix both,

89
00:04:53,860 --> 00:04:54,700
it'll be heaty.

90
00:04:57,140 --> 00:04:57,980
Chief Liu.

91
00:04:58,180 --> 00:04:59,020
Chief Liu.

92
00:04:59,740 --> 00:05:00,580
Chief.

93
00:05:01,460 --> 00:05:02,300
Chief.

94
00:05:02,740 --> 00:05:03,580
Just now,

95
00:05:03,700 --> 00:05:05,020
we took the fish out

96
00:05:05,260 --> 00:05:06,540
and found that it was alive.

97
00:05:06,700 --> 00:05:07,620
It's not dead.

98
00:05:07,860 --> 00:05:08,700
No way.

99
00:05:08,860 --> 00:05:10,020
It's absolutely true.

100
00:05:10,340 --> 00:05:11,180
Look.

101
00:05:19,260 --> 00:05:20,100
Liangyuan.

102
00:05:20,660 --> 00:05:22,380
Maybe you really saw it wrong.

103
00:05:23,340 --> 00:05:24,220
I don't blame you.

104
00:05:24,940 --> 00:05:25,780
But

105
00:05:25,980 --> 00:05:27,180
I'm afraid you can't escape

106
00:05:27,300 --> 00:05:28,340
the one-month salary fine

107
00:05:28,860 --> 00:05:30,060
set by Chief Liu.

108
00:05:33,300 --> 00:05:34,460
This isn't the fish.

109
00:05:35,460 --> 00:05:37,466
- This is the fish.
- This is the fish.

110
00:05:38,740 --> 00:05:41,740
=Episode 26=

111
00:06:04,740 --> 00:06:06,540
I bought some hubings
for you and Xiu'er.

112
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:11,900
I didn't expect you to be at home.

113
00:06:19,288 --> 00:06:21,020
Did the approval process
not go smoothly?

114
00:06:26,020 --> 00:06:27,820
Those in intellectual work rule others.

115
00:06:28,820 --> 00:06:30,740
Those in labor work are ruled by others.

116
00:06:31,380 --> 00:06:32,700
I now understand

117
00:06:34,140 --> 00:06:35,980
how did those in intellectual work

118
00:06:36,420 --> 00:06:37,580
do their work?

119
00:06:40,980 --> 00:06:43,580
Officialdom is like the sea.

120
00:06:44,940 --> 00:06:46,500
Bad swimmers like me

121
00:06:47,380 --> 00:06:48,420
will either drown

122
00:06:48,540 --> 00:06:50,340
or be killed by fish.

123
00:06:52,380 --> 00:06:53,460
If I had known this,

124
00:06:54,020 --> 00:06:55,380
I should have lined my pockets.

125
00:06:55,700 --> 00:06:56,700
Why transport litchis?

126
00:06:58,940 --> 00:07:00,180
You didn't do that

127
00:07:01,333 --> 00:07:03,711
because you're different
from other officials.

128
00:07:03,820 --> 00:07:04,780
You have a conscience.

129
00:07:05,340 --> 00:07:06,300
I have a conscience?

130
00:07:07,500 --> 00:07:09,100
What's the use of having a conscience?

131
00:07:10,140 --> 00:07:11,740
I act with my conscience.

132
00:07:11,866 --> 00:07:13,060
What did I get in return?

133
00:07:14,380 --> 00:07:15,777
I keep running into obstacles.

134
00:07:16,700 --> 00:07:18,060
I should be like

135
00:07:18,460 --> 00:07:19,940
those officials.

136
00:07:19,940 --> 00:07:21,140
Have no conscience.

137
00:07:21,444 --> 00:07:23,600
I should do my best
to line my own pockets

138
00:07:23,644 --> 00:07:24,244
and make money.

139
00:07:25,020 --> 00:07:26,380
At least I can take good care

140
00:07:26,420 --> 00:07:27,260
of my daughter.

141
00:07:28,380 --> 00:07:30,180
Stop saying these discouraging words.

142
00:07:30,466 --> 00:07:32,100
There are many people in Lingnan

143
00:07:32,140 --> 00:07:32,980
who care about you.

144
00:07:33,900 --> 00:07:35,340
You should do them right.

145
00:07:35,500 --> 00:07:36,900
Who's going to do me right then?

146
00:07:38,020 --> 00:07:39,420
Transporting litchis

147
00:07:40,500 --> 00:07:42,540
is next to impossible.

148
00:07:43,580 --> 00:07:44,420
Why

149
00:07:45,380 --> 00:07:46,700
do you all

150
00:07:47,100 --> 00:07:48,300
try to stop me?

151
00:07:49,460 --> 00:07:51,500
He Youguang was willing to kill me.

152
00:07:52,380 --> 00:07:53,820
Alright, we got to Chang'an.

153
00:07:54,980 --> 00:07:57,100
We couldn't submit the petition.

154
00:07:57,540 --> 00:07:59,060
The transport strategy

155
00:07:59,180 --> 00:08:00,300
was tricked out of me.

156
00:08:01,100 --> 00:08:01,940
Why?

157
00:08:02,580 --> 00:08:03,580
Why are people

158
00:08:03,620 --> 00:08:05,460
more vicious than wolves?

159
00:08:06,022 --> 00:08:07,660
Am I the one who wants to eat litchis?

160
00:08:07,900 --> 00:08:08,860
Am I who wants it?

161
00:08:09,822 --> 00:08:11,511
It's His Majesty who wants to eat it.

162
00:08:11,540 --> 00:08:12,420
It's Right Chancellor.

163
00:08:12,420 --> 00:08:13,700
It's Right Chancellor's sister!

164
00:08:13,820 --> 00:08:15,060
His sister wants to eat it!

165
00:08:17,980 --> 00:08:19,140
I worked so hard

166
00:08:19,933 --> 00:08:21,422
to put myself in this situation.

167
00:08:22,420 --> 00:08:23,260
Why?

168
00:08:28,740 --> 00:08:30,066
You don't need to persuade me.

169
00:08:30,066 --> 00:08:31,490
No need to persuade me. I understand.

170
00:08:36,488 --> 00:08:38,080
Are you not transporting litchis
anymore?

171
00:08:38,088 --> 00:08:38,740
No.

172
00:08:40,020 --> 00:08:41,100
No one will help me.

173
00:08:41,466 --> 00:08:42,580
What can we transport?

174
00:08:43,500 --> 00:08:44,340
What can we do?

175
00:08:47,020 --> 00:08:47,980
I'm at my wit's end,

176
00:08:48,660 --> 00:08:49,500
with no way out.

177
00:08:50,980 --> 00:08:51,820
Forget it.

178
00:09:03,820 --> 00:09:05,580
In the past few months,

179
00:09:05,580 --> 00:09:08,340
it feels like there's a big rock
pressing on my chest,

180
00:09:08,340 --> 00:09:09,600
making it hard to breathe.

181
00:09:10,580 --> 00:09:12,420
I just took advantage
of my daughter's absence

182
00:09:12,540 --> 00:09:13,380
to vent some steam.

183
00:09:14,311 --> 00:09:15,666
Sorry to make a fool of myself.

184
00:09:17,300 --> 00:09:18,620
How could I laugh at you?

185
00:09:19,460 --> 00:09:21,220
When I lost my status as leader

186
00:09:22,460 --> 00:09:24,300
and everyone around me
turned against me,

187
00:09:25,620 --> 00:09:26,620
I didn't know

188
00:09:27,140 --> 00:09:29,060
how I could fight against He Youguang

189
00:09:30,300 --> 00:09:32,140
and avenge my father.

190
00:09:34,300 --> 00:09:35,540
But you managed

191
00:09:36,380 --> 00:09:37,580
to revive

192
00:09:37,700 --> 00:09:39,180
a hopeless task.

193
00:09:40,740 --> 00:09:42,500
I didn't give up because of you.

194
00:09:50,355 --> 00:09:52,220
I met Deputy Director Lu a few days ago.

195
00:09:53,222 --> 00:09:54,460
He didn't say it explicitly,

196
00:09:54,500 --> 00:09:55,340
but I knew

197
00:09:57,380 --> 00:09:58,620
I would be useless

198
00:09:59,580 --> 00:10:00,660
before I got evidence,

199
00:10:00,660 --> 00:10:01,820
even if I came to Chang'an.

200
00:10:06,020 --> 00:10:07,220
But I won't give up.

201
00:10:09,260 --> 00:10:10,300
I want to return to Lingnan

202
00:10:10,380 --> 00:10:11,620
and personally get evidence.

203
00:10:14,820 --> 00:10:16,340
I ask you not to give up either.

204
00:10:45,860 --> 00:10:47,044
What brings you here?

205
00:10:48,700 --> 00:10:49,740
I thought about it.

206
00:10:50,420 --> 00:10:51,580
I decided to return to Lingnan

207
00:10:52,260 --> 00:10:53,740
and help Yun Qing get evidence.

208
00:10:55,260 --> 00:10:56,260
Lingnan?

209
00:10:58,780 --> 00:11:00,500
Lingnan is He Youguang's territory.

210
00:11:01,340 --> 00:11:02,940
If you go back, won't you

211
00:11:03,500 --> 00:11:05,222
be walking straight
into the tiger's den?

212
00:11:05,380 --> 00:11:06,660
I still have to protect you.

213
00:11:07,220 --> 00:11:08,820
I thought of a foolproof plan.

214
00:11:09,460 --> 00:11:11,340
If I return to Lingnan under the pretext

215
00:11:11,422 --> 00:11:12,888
of running the litchi transport,

216
00:11:13,340 --> 00:11:14,940
I will be working for His Majesty.

217
00:11:15,540 --> 00:11:16,820
He Youguang won't kill me.

218
00:11:18,100 --> 00:11:20,622
You want to be involved
in Litchi Envoy's transport?

219
00:11:21,260 --> 00:11:24,340
I had fallen out with He Youguang

220
00:11:24,340 --> 00:11:25,420
because of my father,

221
00:11:25,800 --> 00:11:27,488
so I wanted to use this opportunity

222
00:11:27,533 --> 00:11:29,333
to get an identity
that could avoid death.

223
00:11:29,460 --> 00:11:32,700
But Litchi Envoy is being pushed back
and forth by all the government offices,

224
00:11:32,740 --> 00:11:34,180
unable to get official approval.

225
00:11:34,533 --> 00:11:35,900
This plan can't be carried out yet,

226
00:11:37,180 --> 00:11:38,980
So I would like to ask
Deputy Director Lu

227
00:11:39,740 --> 00:11:40,580
to help him out.

228
00:11:42,740 --> 00:11:43,620
Right Chancellor

229
00:11:43,620 --> 00:11:46,133
is holding a grand birthday banquet
for Noble Consort.

230
00:11:46,660 --> 00:11:48,420
Its scale is unprecedented.

231
00:11:48,900 --> 00:11:50,540
He prepared
rare treasures from overseas,

232
00:11:50,900 --> 00:11:52,140
intending to impress everyone

233
00:11:52,300 --> 00:11:53,488
at the birthday banquet.

234
00:11:54,140 --> 00:11:55,620
Lingnan's litchis

235
00:11:55,860 --> 00:11:57,540
just happens to be a rare commodity

236
00:11:57,780 --> 00:11:59,300
that he was in charge of.

237
00:12:00,420 --> 00:12:02,260
If you help Litchi Envoy

238
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:05,740
transport litchis into Chang'an,

239
00:12:06,940 --> 00:12:08,700
we'll be helping Right Chancellor

240
00:12:09,060 --> 00:12:10,340
steal the show.

241
00:12:10,980 --> 00:12:11,940
The litchis' arrival

242
00:12:12,860 --> 00:12:14,100
is nothing but icing on the cake

243
00:12:14,100 --> 00:12:15,260
for Right Chancellor.

244
00:12:15,266 --> 00:12:16,620
But if it can't be transported,

245
00:12:17,020 --> 00:12:18,420
Litchi Envoy will die.

246
00:12:19,180 --> 00:12:20,020
Litchi Envoy

247
00:12:20,420 --> 00:12:22,340
was a minor official in Shanglin Office.

248
00:12:23,180 --> 00:12:24,580
He's honest and loyal.

249
00:12:25,020 --> 00:12:26,340
He took this doomed task

250
00:12:27,260 --> 00:12:29,180
because he was tricked.

251
00:12:30,300 --> 00:12:32,660
He never pocketed any money
when he was in Lingnan.

252
00:12:33,060 --> 00:12:34,860
He only focused
on transporting litchis,

253
00:12:35,540 --> 00:12:37,180
hoping to survive

254
00:12:37,900 --> 00:12:39,620
and live his own life.

255
00:12:42,900 --> 00:12:44,533
We want to overthrow Right Chancellor

256
00:12:45,300 --> 00:12:46,260
so that

257
00:12:46,340 --> 00:12:47,820
no more innocent people

258
00:12:47,820 --> 00:12:49,100
will have to suffer like him.

259
00:12:51,460 --> 00:12:53,180
If we stand by

260
00:12:53,780 --> 00:12:55,500
and watch him die,

261
00:12:56,220 --> 00:12:57,060
how are we different

262
00:12:57,060 --> 00:12:58,300
from the rich and powerful people

263
00:12:58,300 --> 00:12:59,600
who trample on human lives?

264
00:13:01,860 --> 00:13:03,340
What are your chances of success

265
00:13:04,820 --> 00:13:07,100
after your return to Lingnan?

266
00:13:09,140 --> 00:13:10,140
I thought of someone.

267
00:13:10,620 --> 00:13:11,580
He must have

268
00:13:11,660 --> 00:13:13,177
evidence of He Youguang's corruption.

269
00:13:13,340 --> 00:13:14,380
Master Konglang

270
00:13:14,420 --> 00:13:15,720
can't make a move on this person,

271
00:13:16,100 --> 00:13:17,460
but I'm very confident

272
00:13:17,460 --> 00:13:18,777
in making him change sides.

273
00:13:26,100 --> 00:13:26,940
Recently,

274
00:13:27,444 --> 00:13:29,511
I went to Konglang Bookstore
to buy information

275
00:13:30,340 --> 00:13:31,300
and ran into Ma Guiyun.

276
00:13:32,355 --> 00:13:33,900
Was he also there to buy information?

277
00:13:34,300 --> 00:13:35,380
It's not that simple.

278
00:13:36,580 --> 00:13:37,820
He held

279
00:13:37,860 --> 00:13:39,180
a pink round fan.

280
00:13:39,260 --> 00:13:40,100
It's obvious

281
00:13:40,100 --> 00:13:42,060
that it's a gift for a lady.

282
00:13:43,100 --> 00:13:44,380
But the only female member

283
00:13:46,380 --> 00:13:47,620
of Konglang Bookstore

284
00:13:47,660 --> 00:13:50,020
is Master Konglang
who never showed herself.

285
00:13:50,780 --> 00:13:52,900
So Ma Guiyun wants to pursue

286
00:13:52,940 --> 00:13:54,340
